@startuml
actor User
participant Frontend
participant "Auth API" as API
database PostgreSQL
participant SMTP

User -> Frontend: Nhap thong tin dang nhap
Frontend -> API: POST /api/auth/login
API -> PostgreSQL: findUserByEmail
PostgreSQL --> API: user record
API -> API: bcrypt.compare + jwt.sign
API -> PostgreSQL: write audit log
API --> Frontend: token + profile
Frontend --> User: Dang nhap thanh cong
@enduml
